[SN]TITLE[SN]
EU referendum: The European Union in 60 seconds

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
There's a special vote, which is called a referendum, coming up on Thursday 23 June 2016.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 February 2016 Last updated at 12:25 GMT
Adults will be asked to decide whether or not the UK should stay in or leave a club of countries, known as the European Union.
But why is this all happening?
Find out all you need to know about the European Union in Newsround's 60 second guide.
